cs.DB, cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DS

This paper deals with the problem of publishing trajectory data while preserving privacy. This problem is related to data management (cs.DB), privacy and security (cs.CR), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
